criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:
1. Healthcare personnel who are working in the selected Residential care homes (RCHs)
2. Able to read Chinese, and
3. Possess an electronic device (smartphone or tablet) with which to download the BGCTS system.
Exclusion Criteria:
1. Temporary staff who are about to cease employment, be on maternity leave, or go on a long vacation during the data collection period;
2. Students or trainees (including nursing students, physiotherapy students, and health-related trainees), because training institutions are responsible for students' training, and such training may affect students' performance;
3. Volunteer personnel who come to the RCHs at a specific period (for example, to organize activities for the residents during festivals);
4. Clerical and administrative staff, kitchen staff, security staff, and engineering and facilities management staff;
5. Ambulance officers who come to the RCHs to take residents to or from hospitals.
